msgid "Dataset Interpretation"
msgstr "Interpretimi i datasetit"

#: .\templates\analytics\data_quality.html:356
msgid ""
"APP winner companies are distinct procurement winner identifiers derived "
"from APP data."
msgstr "Kompanite fituese APP jane identifikues te dallueshem te fituesve te prokurimit te nxjerre nga te dhenat APP."

#: .\templates\analytics\data_quality.html:357
msgid ""
"Joined companies are APP winner companies that matched QKB subjects by exact "
"normalized NIPT."
msgstr "Kompanite e bashkuara jane kompani fituese APP qe u perputhen me subjekte QKB me NIPT te normalizuar te sakte."

#: .\templates\analytics\data_quality.html:358
msgid ""
"The joined dataset is smaller than the full QKB registry layer because it "
"only contains QKB companies that also appear as APP winner companies."
msgstr "Dataseti i bashkuar eshte me i vogel se shtresa e plote e regjistrit QKB sepse permban vetem kompani QKB qe shfaqen edhe si kompani fituese APP."

#: .\templates\analytics\data_quality.html:359
msgid ""
"OpenCorporates financial enrichment is a secondary subset and should be "
"interpreted as data availability for exploratory analysis."
msgstr "Pasurimi financiar OpenCorporates eshte nje nenset dytesor dhe duhet interpretuar si disponueshmeri te dhenash per analize eksploruese."

#: .\templates\analytics\data_quality.html:360
msgid ""
"Coverage values are based on the current local database state and may change "
"after pipeline reruns."
msgstr "Vlerat e mbulimit bazohen ne gjendjen aktuale te bazes lokale dhe mund te ndryshojne pas riekzekutimeve te pipeline-it."

#: .\templates\analytics\data_quality.html:361
msgid ""
"Missing values should be interpreted in relation to source availability and "
"normalization rules."
msgstr "Vlerat qe mungojne duhet te interpretohen ne raport me disponueshmerine e burimit dhe rregullat e normalizimit."

