msgstr "Disponueshmeria e tabelave te kolektorit"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:12
msgid ""
"Data notes for the Albiz analytical dashboard and joined APP-QKB dataset."
msgstr "Shenime te te dhenave per panelin analitik Albiz dhe datasetin e bashkuar APP-QKB."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:28
#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:57
msgid "Core"
msgstr "Berthame"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:29
#: .\templates\analytics\ml\overview.html:13
#: .\templates\layouts\partials\sidebar.html:87
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Permbledhje"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:33
msgid ""
"Albiz is an academic analytical platform for exploring Albanian APP "
"procurement data, QKB registry coverage, analytical risk indicators, and "
"exploratory ML outputs. It separates collection and analysis into two "
"independent components so the dashboard can remain a read-only "
"interpretation layer."
msgstr "Albiz eshte nje platforme analitike akademike per eksplorimin e te dhenave shqiptare te prokurimit APP, mbulimit te regjistrit QKB, treguesve analitike te riskut dhe rezultateve eksploruese ML. Ajo ndan mbledhjen dhe analizen ne dy komponente te pavarura qe paneli te mbetet nje shtrese interpretimi vetem per lexim."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:39
msgid ""
"Scraper, ETL, feature materialization, profiling, and audit-oriented data "
"pipeline."
msgstr "Scraper, ETL, materializim vecorish, profilizim dhe pipeline te dhenash i orientuar drejt auditimit."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:45
msgid ""
"Django analytics and dashboard layer with read-only access to the collector "
"database."
msgstr "Shtrese analitike dhe panel Django me akses vetem per lexim ne bazen e te dhenave te kolektorit."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:50
msgid ""
"The integration contract between the two components is the database. The "
"dashboard reads materialized collector tables and does not manage collector "
"schema."
msgstr "Kontrata e integrimit midis dy komponenteve eshte baza e te dhenave. Paneli lexon tabelat e materializuara te kolektorit dhe nuk menaxhon skemen e tij."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:58
msgid "Data Sources"
msgstr "Burimet e te dhenave"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:64
msgid "APP procurement exports"
msgstr "Eksporte prokurimi APP"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:65
msgid ""
"Public procurement records are used to identify winner companies and "
"procurement activity patterns."
msgstr "Regjistrat publike te prokurimit perdoren per te identifikuar kompanite fituese dhe modelet e aktivitetit te prokurimit."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:70
msgid "QKB registry lookup data"
msgstr "Te dhena kerkimi te regjistrit QKB"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:71
msgid ""
"Business registry search and lookup data provide company-level registry "
"attributes for joined subjects."
msgstr "Te dhenat e kerkimit ne regjistrin e biznesit japin atribute regjistri ne nivel kompanie per subjektet e bashkuara."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:77
msgid "Experimental"
msgstr "Eksperimentale"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:78
msgid "QKB historical discovery"
msgstr "Zbulim historik QKB"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:80
msgid ""
"Historical extract and document discovery are exploratory in the current "
"version and are not yet fully batch-extracted."
msgstr "Ekstraktet historike dhe zbulimi i dokumenteve jane eksploruese ne versionin aktual dhe ende nuk jane nxjerre plotesisht ne grup."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:86
msgid "Secondary"
msgstr "Dytesore"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:89
msgid ""
"OpenCorporates is treated only as secondary exploratory enrichment, not as "
"the QKB registry backbone or complete financial coverage."
msgstr "OpenCorporates trajtohet vetem si pasurim dytesor eksplorues, jo si shtrese baze e regjistrit QKB ose mbulim financiar i plote."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:98
msgid "Pipeline"
msgstr "Pipeline"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:99
msgid "Data Pipeline"
msgstr "Pipeline i te dhenave"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:105
msgid "1. Raw fetch"
msgstr "1. Marrja bruto"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:106
msgid "Source files and responses are collected by the pipeline."
msgstr "Skedaret burimore dhe pergjigjet mblidhen nga pipeline-i."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:111
msgid "2. Raw storage"
msgstr "2. Ruajtja bruto"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:112
msgid "Content hashing supports reproducibility and change detection."
msgstr "Hashimi i permbajtjes mbeshtet riprodhueshmerine dhe zbulimin e ndryshimeve."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:117
msgid "3. Normalization"
msgstr "3. Normalizimi"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:118
msgid "Identifiers, dates, amounts, and labels are standardized for analysis."
msgstr "Identifikuesit, datat, shumat dhe etiketat standardizohen per analize."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:123
msgid "4. Feature materialization"
msgstr "4. Materializimi i vecorive"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:124
msgid ""
"Company-level feature tables are built for APP, QKB, and joined records."
msgstr "Tabelat e vecorive ne nivel kompanie ndertohen per APP, QKB dhe regjistrat e bashkuar."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:129
msgid "5. Profiling and audit"
msgstr "5. Profilizim dhe auditim"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:130
msgid ""
"Row counts, joins, and coverage metrics are checked after pipeline runs."
msgstr "Numrat e rreshtave, bashkimet dhe metrikat e mbulimit kontrollohen pas ekzekutimeve te pipeline-it."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:135
msgid "6. Dashboard access"
msgstr "6. Akses ne panel"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:136
msgid ""
"Django reads the materialized tables through the collector database alias."
msgstr "Django lexon tabelat e materializuara permes alias-it te bazes se kolektorit."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:145
msgid "Definitions"
msgstr "Perkufizime"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:146
msgid "Analytical Definitions"
msgstr "Perkufizime analitike"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:152
msgid "Procurement-based performance proxy"
msgstr "Perafrim i performances se bazuar ne prokurime"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:154
msgid ""
"Company performance in this dashboard means activity observed in APP "
"procurement data, such as active procurement count, winner value, authority "
"diversity, and active year span. It is not a full financial-performance "
"measure."
msgstr "Performanca e kompanise ne kete panel nenkupton aktivitetin e vezhguar ne te dhenat e prokurimit APP, si numri i prokurimeve aktive, vlera fituese, diversiteti i autoriteteve dhe shtrirja aktive ne vite. Nuk eshte mase e plote e performances financiare."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:160
msgid "Analytical risk indicators"
msgstr "Tregues analitike te riskut"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:162
msgid ""
"Risk indicators are heuristic analytical flags for prioritizing review. They "
"are not evidence for legal findings or administrative determinations."
msgstr "Treguesit e riskut jane flamuj analitike heuristike per prioritizim shqyrtimi. Ata nuk jane prove per gjetje ligjore ose vendime administrative."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:172
msgid "Core join"
msgstr "Bashkim berthame"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:173
msgid "Exact NIPT Matching"
msgstr "Perputhje e sakte e NIPT-it"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:177
msgid ""
"APP winners and QKB subjects are joined only by exact normalized NIPT/NUIS. "
"No fuzzy matching is used for the core joined dataset."
msgstr "Fituesit APP dhe subjektet QKB bashkohen vetem me NIPT/NUIS te normalizuar te sakte. Nuk perdoret perputhje e paqarte per datasetin kryesor te bashkuar."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:180
msgid "Exact matching reduces false positive links between unrelated entities."
msgstr "Perputhja e sakte ul lidhjet pozitive te rreme midis entiteteve te palidhura."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:181
msgid ""
"The joined dataset contains companies that appear in both APP procurement "
"data and QKB registry data."
msgstr "Dataseti i bashkuar permban kompani qe shfaqen si ne te dhenat e prokurimit APP ashtu edhe ne te dhenat e regjistrit QKB."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:182
msgid ""
"Records with missing, malformed, or inconsistent identifiers may remain "
"unmatched."
msgstr "Regjistrat me identifikues qe mungojne, jane te keqformuar ose jokonsistente mund te mbeten te paperputhur."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:189
#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:92
#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:129
#: .\templates\analytics\risk_overview.html:266
msgid "Indicators"
msgstr "Tregues"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:194
msgid ""
"Risk indicators are computed analytical signals that help prioritize "
"entities for further review. They are not legal findings or determinations."
msgstr "Treguesit e riskut jane sinjale analitike te llogaritura qe ndihmojne ne prioritizimin e subjekteve per shqyrtim te metejshem. Ata nuk jane gjetje ose vendime ligjore."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:213
msgid "Exploratory ML Methodology"
msgstr "Metodologji eksploruese ML"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:217
msgid ""
"ML outputs are built from generated files under <code>reports/ml/</code> and "
"are not trained inside page views. The models are exploratory tools for "
"understanding heuristic labels and procurement-profile structure."
msgstr "Rezultatet ML ndertohen nga skedare te gjeneruar nen <code>reports/ml/</code> dhe nuk trajnohen brenda pamjeve te faqeve. Modelet jane mjete eksploruese per te kuptuar etiketat heuristike dhe strukturen e profilit te prokurimit."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:220
msgid ""
"Weak-label classification measures agreement with constructed heuristic "
"labels, not external ground truth."
msgstr "Klasifikimi me etiketa te dobeta mat perputhjen me etiketa heuristike te ndertuara, jo me te verteta te jashtme."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:221
msgid ""
"The reduced-feature strict-label experiment excludes direct label-defining "
"fields as much as possible to reduce circularity."
msgstr "Eksperimenti me vecori te reduktuara dhe etikete strikte perjashton sa me shume fusha qe percaktojne etiketen per te ulur rrethorin."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:222
msgid ""
"Isolation Forest and Local Outlier Factor provide statistical anomaly "
"rankings for unusual procurement profiles."
msgstr "Isolation Forest dhe Local Outlier Factor japin renditje statistikore anomalish per profile te pazakonta prokurimi."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:223
msgid ""
"KMeans clustering and PCA summarize procurement-profile structure for "
"interpretation and visualization."
msgstr "Grupimi KMeans dhe PCA permbledhin strukturen e profilit te prokurimit per interpretim dhe vizualizim."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:224
msgid ""
"The financial enrichment subset experiment compares procurement-only "
"features with secondary OpenCorporates financial features where coverage "
"exists."
msgstr "Eksperimenti i nensetit te pasurimit financiar krahason vecorite vetem te prokurimit me vecori financiare dytesore OpenCorporates aty ku ka mbulim."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:231
msgid "Exploratory"
msgstr "Eksploruese"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:236
msgid ""
"Visual Analytics summarizes distributions by legal form, city, registration "
"year, procurement activity, winner value, winner/budget ratio bands, and "
"risk indicator distribution. These views are exploratory results based on "
"joined APP-QKB companies."
msgstr "Analitika vizuale permbledh shperndarjet sipas formes ligjore, qytetit, vitit te regjistrimit, aktivitetit te prokurimit, vleres fituese, brezave te raportit fitues/buxhet dhe shperndarjes se treguesve te riskut. Keto pamje jane rezultate eksploruese bazuar ne kompanite e bashkuara APP-QKB."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:245
msgid "Current profile"
msgstr "Profili aktual"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:246
msgid "Dataset Scope"
msgstr "Shtrirja e datasetit"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:249
msgid ""
"Current local dataset/profile values. These may change after future pipeline "
"reruns."
msgstr "Vlerat aktuale lokale te datasetit/profilit. Keto mund te ndryshojne pas riekzekutimeve te ardhshme te pipeline-it."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:254
msgid "APP/procurement winner companies"
msgstr "Kompani fituese APP/prokurimi"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:259
msgid "around 59,266"
msgstr "rreth 59,266"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:266
msgid "QKB match rate over APP winner companies"
msgstr "Norma e perputhjes QKB mbi kompanite fituese APP"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:267
#, python-format
msgid "around 99.3%%"
msgstr "rreth 99.3%%"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:277
#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:278
#: .\templates\analytics\ml\model_card.html:161
#: .\templates\analytics\registry_enrichment.html:385
msgid "Limitations"
msgstr "Kufizime"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:282
msgid ""
"Public source completeness depends on source availability and publication "
"formats."
msgstr "Plotesia e burimeve publike varet nga disponueshmeria e burimit dhe formatet e publikimit."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:283
msgid ""
"Exact NIPT matching may miss records with missing or incorrect identifiers."
msgstr "Perputhja e sakte e NIPT-it mund te humbase regjistra me identifikues qe mungojne ose jane te pasakte."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:284
msgid "Some APP records have missing winner NIPT values."
msgstr "Disa regjistra APP kane vlera NIPT fituesi qe mungojne."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:285
msgid ""
"QKB historical documents are not fully batch-extracted in the current "
"version."
msgstr "Dokumentet historike QKB nuk jane nxjerre plotesisht ne grup ne versionin aktual."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:286
msgid "Scanned PDFs and OCR are not part of the core pipeline."
msgstr "PDF-te e skanuara dhe OCR nuk jane pjese e pipeline-it kryesor."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:287
msgid ""
"OpenCorporates financial data is incomplete, secondary, and should be "
"validated against source filings where required."
msgstr "Te dhenat financiare OpenCorporates jane te paplota, dytesore dhe duhet te verifikohen kundrejt depozitimeve burimore kur kerkohet."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:288
msgid "There is no official ground-truth risk label in this version."
msgstr "Ne kete version nuk ka etikete zyrtare te vertete risku."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:289
msgid ""
"Risk indicators and ML outputs are heuristic analytical signals that require "
"human interpretation and future validation."
msgstr "Treguesit e riskut dhe rezultatet ML jane sinjale analitike heuristike qe kerkojne interpretim njerezor dhe validim te ardhshem."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:296
msgid "Future work"
msgstr "Pune e ardhshme"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:297
msgid "Future Work"
msgstr "Pune e ardhshme"

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:301
msgid "QKB historical document link extraction."
msgstr "Nxjerrja e lidhjeve te dokumenteve historike QKB."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:302
msgid "Financial document parsing from XLSX where available."
msgstr "Parsimi i dokumenteve financiare nga XLSX aty ku jane te disponueshme."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:303
msgid "OCR as optional future work for scanned documents."
msgstr "OCR si pune opsionale e ardhshme per dokumentet e skanuara."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:304
msgid "More advanced statistical and ML models."
msgstr "Modele statistikore dhe ML me te avancuara."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:305
msgid "Exportable analytical reports."
msgstr "Raporte analitike te eksportueshme."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:306
msgid "Read-only user roles and deployment hardening."
msgstr "Role perdoruesish vetem per lexim dhe forcim i vendosjes ne prodhim."

#: .\templates\analytics\methodology.html:313
msgid "Related Views"
msgstr "Pamje te lidhura"

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:4
msgid "ML Anomaly Detection"
msgstr "Zbulimi ML i anomalive"

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:7
#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:9
#: .\templates\analytics\ml\exports.html:56
#: .\templates\analytics\ml\overview.html:279
#: .\templates\layouts\partials\sidebar.html:93
msgid "Anomaly Detection"
msgstr "Zbulimi i anomalive"

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:8
msgid ""
"Unsupervised anomaly rankings and concrete procurement-profile visualization "
"for exploratory review."
msgstr "Renditje anomalish pa mbikeqyrje dhe vizualizim konkret i profilit te prokurimit per shqyrtim eksplorues."

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:20
msgid ""
"Isolation Forest identifies statistically unusual company profiles in the "
"prepared feature space. It is unsupervised and does not use official event "
"labels as a target."
msgstr "Isolation Forest identifikon profile kompanish statistikisht te pazakonta ne hapesiren e pergatitur te vecorive. Eshte pa mbikeqyrje dhe nuk perdor etiketa zyrtare ngjarjesh si objektiv."

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:30
msgid ""
"Local Outlier Factor highlights local-neighborhood outliers. It is useful "
"for exploratory anomaly ranking and requires human review."
msgstr "Local Outlier Factor thekson vlera jashte norme ne lagje lokale. Eshte i dobishem per renditje eksploruese anomalish dhe kerkon shqyrtim njerezor."

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:41
msgid "3D Procurement Anomaly Cube"
msgstr "Kubi 3D i anomalive te prokurimit"

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:42
msgid ""
"Interactive 3D view of procurement activity, procurement value, and anomaly "
"intensity."
msgstr "Pamje interaktive 3D e aktivitetit te prokurimit, vleres se prokurimit dhe intensitetit te anomalise."

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:44
msgid "Log scaling used for readability"
msgstr "Shkalle logaritmike per lexueshmeri"

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:48
msgid ""
"This chart highlights statistically unusual procurement profiles for "
"exploratory review. It is not evidence for legal or administrative "
"conclusions."
msgstr "Ky grafik thekson profile prokurimi statistikisht te pazakonta per shqyrtim eksplorues. Nuk eshte prove per perfundime ligjore ose administrative."

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:53
msgid "Axes"
msgstr "Boshtet"

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:63
#: .\templates\analytics\ml\overview.html:244
msgid "Interpretation"
msgstr "Interpretimi"

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:64
msgid ""
"Higher Z values indicate a more unusual procurement profile according to the "
"anomaly model. Marker size reflects procurement-based performance score "
"where available. Results require human review and source verification."
msgstr "Vlerat me te larta Z tregojne profil me te pazakonte prokurimi sipas modelit te anomalise. Madhesia e shenjuesit reflekton rezultatin e performances se bazuar ne prokurim kur eshte i disponueshem. Rezultatet kerkojne shqyrtim njerezor dhe verifikim burimi."

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:68
msgid ""
"Procurement anomaly cube data is unavailable in the current generated "
"outputs."
msgstr "Te dhenat e kubit te anomalive te prokurimit nuk jane te disponueshme ne rezultatet aktuale te gjeneruara."

#: .\templates\analytics\ml\anomaly.html:70
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Showing a deterministic capped sample of %(count)s companies. Source data is "
